    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >款简短的电影风格西部射击游戏，充满狂野而快速的扫射式动作！帮助一位射击高手的叛逆者完成接管酒馆的任务。先开枪，永远不问。清除所有胆敢挡在你面前的人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A brutal showdown awaits. It’s you against the entire town!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313230/extras/bdd101e522cdb2377f9842ef7d809939.avif?t=1734456756\" width=600 height=441 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle through four ruthless gangs that control the saloon and claim your place as the ultimate gunslinger. Only one can come out on top. Get ready for the fight of your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Origins of the Saloon King</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was originally submitted to Jern Jam 3. I was so happy with the result, plus it won an award for <i>Cinematography &amp; Completeness</i> that I decided to expand and improve it. I'm excited to share the updated version on Steam as a freebie!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
